flowchart LR
  CHG[Product Change] --> QG[Automated Quality Gates\nBuild, security, tests]
  QG --> DEP[Controlled Cloud Deployment\nSigned artifacts + rollout safety]
  DEP --> SMK[Smoke Validation\nFast post-deploy checks]
  SMK --> E2E[Full End-to-End Validation]
  E2E --> COV[Coverage + Journey Verification]
  COV --> MON[Ongoing Health Monitoring\nDaily and post-deploy checks]
  MON --> CONF[Release Confidence\nTrust signal for teams and stakeholders]

  SMK -->|Failure| RB[Fast Rollback]
  E2E -->|Failure| RB
  COV -->|Failure| RB
